natspec.details: Common mathematical functions used in both PRBMathSD59x18 and PRBMathUD60x18. Note that this shared library does not always assume the signed 59.18-decimal fixed-point or the unsigned 60.18-decimal fixed-point representation. When it does not, it is explicitly mentioned in the NatSpec documentation.

SCALE.details: How many trailing decimals can be represented.

SCALE_LPOTD.details: Largest power of two divisor of SCALE.
